555
00:46:46,012 --> 00:46:47,347
Kita berlawan dulu.

556
00:46:51,392 --> 00:46:52,227
Tak guna!

557
00:46:57,482 --> 00:46:58,650
Hidung saya.

558
00:47:05,281 --> 00:47:06,449
