Itu saja suka-suka.

643
00:52:16,801 --> 00:52:17,635
Memang nakal.

644
00:52:19,929 --> 00:52:22,348
Jerry, awak di sana? Sila jawab.

645
00:52:22,932 --> 00:52:24,684
Jerry, saya terima panggilan.

646
00:52:24,767 --> 00:52:28,646
Sawtooth dilihat bersendirian,
