674
00:55:16,272 --> 00:55:18,649
Mereka ingat mereka dapat lari.

675
00:55:21,444 --> 00:55:23,446
Begitulah kisahnya.

676
00:55:36,083 --> 00:55:36,917
Lari!

677
00:55:38,753 --> 00:55:39,587
